    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm not talking about a bender or anything lol. just like, a single glass of wine to help with the anxiety so the pill actually works? it's just a little bit, i don't think it would be a big deal if i'm just staying in bed all night. wouldn't it just make the relaxation effect a bit stronger?",
