      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just seems like a lot of caution for literally one glass. i've heard people do this all the time and they're fine. if i just take a very small amount of both, it's basically just more of a sedative, right? it's not like i'm taking a whole bottle. can't it just be used to help the pill work more effectively if i'm really stressed?",
